                alt="windows-pre-commit-output" class="[ w-full ]" />
        </figure>
      </How>

      <Summary>
        <p>
          Automating Git hook setup with <Highlight>MSBuild</Highlight> simplifies project configuration and ensures consistency across 
          all developer machines. By leveraging a custom target in the <Highlight>.csproj</Highlight> file, you can efficiently set up 
          pre-commit hooks without requiring manual intervention, improving both productivity and team collaboration.
        </p>
      </Summary>
    </ContentBody>
</Content>